column1: query

SELECT individual_id FROM Individuals WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Organization_Contact_Individuals WHERE individual_id > 7 AND Individuals.individual_id = Organization_Contact_Individuals.individual_id) LIMIT 4
SELECT individual_first_name FROM Individuals WHERE individual_id >= 33 ORDER BY individual_first_name ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT x.date_contact_to), x.individual_id FROM Organization_Contact_Individuals AS x WHERE x.individual_id < 6 AND date_contact_from > (SELECT MAX(date_contact_from) FROM Organization_Contact_Individuals WHERE individual_id != 60)
SELECT Forms.form_id FROM Forms JOIN Party_Forms ON Forms.form_id = Party_Forms.form_id WHERE  Forms.form_id = 92 LIMIT 4

SELECT AVG(individual_id), COUNT(DISTINCT individual_id) FROM Organization_Contact_Individuals WHERE (individual_id, organization_id) IN (SELECT individual_id, organization_id FROM Organization_Contact_Individuals WHERE individual_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND individual_id >= 36 ORDER BY date_contact_from LIMIT 6)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT date_formed), Organization_Contact_Individuals.organization_id FROM Organization_Contact_Individuals JOIN Organizations ON Organizations.organization_id = Organization_Contact_Individuals.organization_id WHERE individual_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  Organization_Contact_Individuals.organization_id <= 13
SELECT form_type_code, form_type_code FROM Forms JOIN Services ON Forms.service_id = Services.service_id WHERE  form_id <= 38

SELECT SUM(Forms.service_id), Forms.form_id FROM Forms JOIN Party_Forms ON Forms.form_id = Party_Forms.form_id WHERE Party_Forms.form_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Forms.form_number <= (SELECT AVG(form_number) FROM Forms)

SELECT customer_id FROM Party_Services JOIN Services ON Party_Services.service_id = Services.service_id JOIN Party_Forms ON Party_Services.customer_id = Party_Forms.party_id JOIN Parties ON Party_Forms.party_id = Parties.party_id WHERE booking_id > 14 ORDER BY customer_id ASC LIMIT 1
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT service_id), form_type_code FROM Forms WHERE service_id >= 93 GROUP BY form_type_code ORDER BY form_type_code DESC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT party_id) FROM Party_Addresses WHERE  address_id <= 32 LIMIT 4
SELECT party_id, address_type_code, date_address_to FROM Party_Addresses WHERE  address_id < 62 GROUP BY date_address_to HAVING MIN(party_id) > 67 LIMIT 2
SELECT date_fully_completed, MAX(party_id) FROM Party_Forms WHERE form_id != 23 OR form_id IN (SELECT form_id FROM Party_Forms WHERE form_id > 68 LIMIT 10) GROUP BY date_fully_completed
SELECT x.party_id FROM Parties AS x WHERE x.party_id BETWEEN 1 AND 49;

SELECT form_type_code FROM Forms JOIN Party_Forms ON Forms.form_id = Party_Forms.form_id JOIN Parties ON Parties.party_id = Party_Forms.party_id JOIN Party_Services ON Party_Services.customer_id = Parties.party_id WHERE Party_Forms.form_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND booking_id != 84 LIMIT 9

SELECT T1.service_id FROM Party_Services AS T1 JOIN Party_Forms AS T2 ON T1.customer_id = T2.party_id JOIN Parties AS T3 ON T3.party_id = T2.party_id WHERE T1.booking_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR T1.customer_id = 38
SELECT COUNT(e.service_id), COUNT(DISTINCT e.service_id) FROM Forms AS e WHERE  e.form_id >= 41
SELECT COUNT(address_id), party_id FROM Party_Addresses WHERE  party_id <= 29 ORDER BY party_id ASC

SELECT f.individual_last_name, f.individual_email FROM Individuals AS f JOIN Individuals AS i ON i.individual_id = f.individual_id WHERE f.individual_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Organization_Contact_Individuals WHERE organization_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND f.individual_id = individual_id) GROUP BY f.individual_email ORDER BY f.individual_email ASC LIMIT 9
SELECT COUNT(p.form_id), COUNT(DISTINCT p.form_status_code), COUNT(DISTINCT p.party_id) FROM Party_Forms AS p WHERE  p.form_id = 7
SELECT h.organization_id FROM Organization_Contact_Individuals AS h WHERE  h.organization_id != 49

SELECT COUNT(Services.service_id), Party_Services.booking_id FROM Forms INNER JOIN Party_Services ON Forms.service_id = Party_Services.service_id INNER JOIN Services ON Forms.service_id = Services.service_id WHERE Forms.service_id < 56 ORDER BY Party_Services.booking_id DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Services.service_id), Services.service_description, Forms.form_number FROM Forms JOIN Party_Services JOIN Services ON Forms.service_id = Services.service_id AND Services.service_id = Party_Services.service_id WHERE customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR form_name NOT IN (SELECT form_name FROM Forms WHERE  form_id != 4 LIMIT 4)
SELECT MIN(service_id), service_id, form_name FROM Forms WHERE form_id = 90 GROUP BY form_name, service_id

SELECT Organizations.organization_id, uk_vat_number FROM Organization_Contact_Individuals JOIN Organizations ON Organizations.organization_id = Organization_Contact_Individuals.organization_id WHERE Organization_Contact_Individuals.organization_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10

SELECT MAX(Forms.service_id), MIN(Party_Forms.form_id) FROM Forms JOIN Party_Services JOIN Party_Forms JOIN Parties ON Parties.party_id = Party_Forms.party_id AND Forms.form_id = Party_Forms.form_id AND Party_Services.customer_id = Parties.party_id WHERE Party_Forms.form_id < 38 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Forms AS F WHERE F.service_id > 11 AND F.form_id = Party_Forms.form_id)
SELECT SUM(form_id) FROM Forms LIMIT 5
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT uk_vat_number), organization_name FROM Organizations WHERE  organization_id > 42

SELECT AVG(Party_Forms.party_id), booking_id 
                    FROM Party_Services 
                    JOIN Parties ON Party_Services.customer_id = Parties.party_id 
                    JOIN Party_Forms ON Parties.party_id = Party_Forms.party_id 
                    WHERE service_id = 18 
                    LIMIT 7

SELECT k.service_type_code, k.service_type_code, k.service_name FROM Services AS k WHERE k.service_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND service_type_code IN (SELECT service_type_code FROM Services AS j WHERE  j.service_id != 86)
